                        </h3>
                        <button onclick="closeModal()"
                            class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
                            <i class="fas fa-times text-xl"></i>
                        </button>
